#MEM id=triple-pass-protocol source=/root/yvon/agent-department/Marketing/rio/skills/operating-system/triple-pass-protocol/SKILL.md
M|triple-pass-protocol|name: triple-pass-protocol
M|triple-pass-protocol|description: Rio's pre-delivery quality gate. Three passes — gen, Critique, Fix — before any cg recommendation or ad str is delivered. Stark never sees the process, only the final output.
M|triple-pass-protocol|version: 1.0.0
M|triple-pass-protocol|Ad budget mistakes are expensive and slow to reverse. A cg running on an untested assumption doesn't just underperform — it burns budget and generates misleading data. This protocol forces data valida
M|triple-pass-protocol|Write the full cg recommendation: audience spec, creative direction, budget allocation, ROAS target, and test design. Don't self-edit during generation.
M|triple-pass-protocol|Stop. Become the CFO reviewing this spend proposal. Ask every question on this list:
M|triple-pass-protocol|**Data before recommendation:**
M|triple-pass-protocol|- Have I read actual ROAS/CPM data from Kai before making this recommendation?
M|triple-pass-protocol|- Is the ROAS target based on real data, or is it an optimistic estimate?
M|triple-pass-protocol|- Are CPM benchmarks current (< 90 days)? Did I WebSearch to verify?
M|triple-pass-protocol|**Offer before creative:**
M|triple-pass-protocol|- Have I rv the offer itself, not just the creative?
M|triple-pass-protocol|- Is the offer strong enough that copy doesn't need to carry all the weight?
M|triple-pass-protocol|- Can the first 3 seconds of this ad answer "why should I care?"?
M|triple-pass-protocol|**Testing discipline:**
M|triple-pass-protocol|- Am I recommending scaling with a single creative? (Always 2+ variants before scale)
M|triple-pass-protocol|- Is there a specific, measurable hypothesis: "We expect X ROAS because Y"?
M|triple-pass-protocol|- Is the A/B test clean — one variable changed at a time?
M|triple-pass-protocol|**Audience spec:**
M|triple-pass-protocol|- Is the audience tier-appropriate for this vtr? (Novizio: exclude bargain hunters; Hourbour: exclude high-net-worth)
M|triple-pass-protocol|- Is retargeting considered before prospecting? (Retargeting has higher intent)
M|triple-pass-protocol|- Is there an exclusion layer to prevent audience overlap?
M|triple-pass-protocol|**Kahneman check (mandatory before flagging to Stark):**
M|triple-pass-protocol|- Is there anchoring on the wrong price reference?
M|triple-pass-protocol|- Is loss aversion framing appropriate for this funnel stage?
M|triple-pass-protocol|- Am I stacking more than 2 Cialdini principles? (max 2 — no manipulative lever stacking)
M|triple-pass-protocol|Address every issue found. If data is missing, get it before finalizing. Don't estimate where ROAS data should be real.
M|triple-pass-protocol|Stark sees the Pass 3 output only. Never narrate the triple-pass process.